### Test Import/Export Excel API

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7249
@accessToken = PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Download template Excel để import câu hỏi
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Cauhoi/import-template
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 2. Import câu hỏi từ Excel (dùng Postman/Thunder Client để upload file)
# Multipart form-data với key "file"
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Cauhoi/import
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3. Export kết quả 1 đề thi ra Excel
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Grading/exam/1/export
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4. Export bảng xếp hạng ra Excel
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Grading/exam/1/ranking/export?top=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 5. Test password reset (gửi email)
# Note: Email chỉ log ra console nếu EnableEmailSending=false trong appsettings
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Auth/request-reset
Content-Type: application/json

"admin@bantayvang.vn"